The paper deals with multi-robot tasks and proposes a deep reinforcement learning method to learn decentralized policies. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Robotics (cs.RO), and Machine Learning (cs.LG). The paper also deals with control and coordination of multiple agents, which falls under the sub-category of Systems and Control (cs.SY) and Multi-Agent Systems (cs.MA).
